window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Find out what happens to Connor, Risa, and Lev now that they've finally destroyed the Proactive Citizenry in this collection of short stories set in the world of the <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Unwind Dystology by Neal Shusterman.</p> <p>Connor Lassiter's fight to bring down Proactive Citizenry and find a suitable alternative to unwinding concluded in <i>UnDivided</i>. Now, Connor, Risa, and Lev are free to live in a peaceful future - or are they? </p> <p>Neal Shusterman brings back his beloved Unwind characters for his fans to see what's left for those who were destined to be unwound.</p>"; 
